  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start the day with the delicious buffet breakfast which includes an excellent range of hot and cold items. Weekend breakfasts are upgraded to <strong>Jungle Room Brunch</strong> experiences, including champagne and a live DJ.</p>
<p>In the evening you'll enjoy either a three-course served meal with choices of main dish, or a buffet meal. The Bled Rose chef is a member of the Slovenian Culinary Team and has won many awards. His philosophy is to use only first-class and local ingredients, melding a range of flavours and culinary styles from around the world.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
