  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Bled Rose Hotel is a popular four-star hotel close to the lakeshore and the town centre. Relax in stylish luxury, and enjoy views towards Lake Bled and over Zdraviliški Park towards Bled Castle.</p>
<h2>Stylish interiors and an excellent spa</h2>
<p>The hotel's chic lobby and bright rooms offer comfort and modern design. The indoor swimming pool, outdoor whirlpool and relaxation loungers are the perfect spot to relax at the end of a day exploring. As optional extras (payable locally) you can also enjoy the 'Sauna World' or, if you want to really treat yourself, book a VIP spa room. These have a private whirlpool and sauna, and the package includes either a massage or colour therapy (Chromotherapy).</p>
<h2>Enjoy local produce and delicious Slovenian cuisine</h2>
<p>The staff are always friendly and helpful, and the meals are excellent. On sunny days enjoy breakfast and dinner on the large terrace. The restaurant combines modern trends (including jungle themed buffet area) with traditional Slovenian cuisine and prides itself on using premium local ingredients and fresh produce.</p>]]></description>
