  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Outdoor whirlpool</li>
<li>Relaxation area</li>
<li>Fitness studio</li>
<li>Sauna world with two Finnish and one Turkish sauna (payable locally - approx. €19 per person per use)</li>
<li>VIP spa rooms where you can enjoy private pampering for two. Each room has a whirlpool, sauna, two massage tables and a fridge (payable locally)</li>
<li>Massage treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Chromotherapy - a colour therapy that uses different light spectrums (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Garden</li>
<li>Sun terrace with sun loungers</li>
<li>Parking (garage spaces also available - approx. €10 per night)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots &amp; linen available (approx. €10 per cot per stay - payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
