  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin/Double With Balcony</strong> are around 15m² and sleep two people. Some rooms are available with a balcony for a supplement. Rooms can be made up as a double or twin - please request at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Twin/Double Without Balcony</strong> are around 15m² and sleep two people. These rooms can also be booked for single occupancy and are available on request only - please call us to book. Rooms can be made up as a double or twin - please let us know at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Lakeside Twin or Double Rooms</strong> are around 18m² and sleep two people. These rooms face the lake and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Double Rooms</strong> are around 31m² and can sleep two to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). These rooms are lake-facing and have a lounge area and a balcony. These rooms are available on request - please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air Conditioning</li>
<li>Kettle (available on request)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>2pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €3.13 per adult per night is payable locally. Children aged 7-17 years pay a discounted rate of approx. €1.57 per night, and children aged 6 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
